import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Patient } from 'src/app/Models/Patient'; import { HttpService } from 'src/app/Services/http.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-patients', templateUrl: './patients.component.html', styleUrls: ['./patients.component.css'] }) export class PatientsComponent { listofpat :Patient[]; constructor(private httpservice: HttpService){ this.httpservice.getPatientsCabinet(this.httpservice.md.nom_cabinet).subscribe((result: Patient[])=>{ this.listofpat=result; console.log(this.listofpat); }, (error)=>{ //this.router.navigate(["/Admin"]); alert("wa l3adaw rah majach"); } ); } }
